    <title>参加2018全国才艺展演活动</title>
    <link href="http://daughter.tonybai.com/2018/08/18/national-guzheng-performance-20180818/"/>
    <id>http://daughter.tonybai.com/2018/08/18/national-guzheng-performance-20180818/</id>
    <published>2018-08-18T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-27T00:29:31.778Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>暑假已经过去大半了。在暑假接近尾声的时候，妈妈带我去北京参加了“2018全国才艺展演活动”，和我同行的还有我的古筝老师陈老师以及一起学古筝的小伙伴们。</p>
<p>在这次为期四天的才艺展演之行中，我见到了我的古筝偶像们，她们是著名古筝大师<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8E%8B%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%80/6288907?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="external">王天一</a>以及他的几名高徒：<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B5%B5%E5%8B%83%E6%A5%A0/2325903?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="external">赵勃楠</a>、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8E%8B%E5%86%AC%E5%A9%89/2325968?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="external">王冬婉</a>和<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A7%9C%E6%B7%BC/70183" target="_blank" rel="external">姜淼</a>。按照老妈的说法，这次活动大大提升了我对古筝演奏的兴趣。在这次展演活动中，我表演了十级曲目“伊犁河畔”，并得到了组委会颁发的金奖。</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_1.jpg" alt="金奖奖杯"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_2.jpg" alt="金奖证书"></p>
<p>活动结束后，还有一天的自由活动时间，我们一起去了中国科技馆玩了一天。显然在科技馆这种地方，还是和老爸一起玩比较好，按照老爸的说法：老妈的科学素养还有很大提升空间。下面是此次北京之旅的一些照片，请您欣赏^_^。</p>
<p>8月16日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180816_1.jpg" alt="高铁出发"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180816_2.jpg" alt="到达目的地"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180816_3.jpg" alt="到达目的地1"></p>
<p>8月17日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_1.jpg" alt="展演选手集体合影"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_2.jpg" alt="我和小伙伴儿1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_3.jpg" alt="我和小伙伴儿2"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_4.jpg" alt="化妆后候场1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_5.jpg" alt="化妆后候场2"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_6.jpg" alt="表演中1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_7.jpg" alt="表演中2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_8.jpg" alt="表演中3"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_9.jpg" alt="表演后1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_10.jpg" alt="表演后2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_11.jpg" alt="表演后3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_12.jpg" alt="表演后4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_13.jpg" alt="表演后5"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_14.jpg" alt="表演后6"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_15.jpg" alt="表演后7"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_16.jpg" alt="晚上参加独奏音乐会"></p>
<p>8月18日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_3.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_4.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_5.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_6.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_7.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅5"></p>
<p>晚上我们参加了另外一场古筝名家的演奏会，我与我的几位偶像都合了影，太开心了！</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_8.jpg" alt="与姜淼老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_9.jpg" alt="与王冬婉老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_10.jpg" alt="与赵勃楠老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_11.jpg" alt="参加了另外一场古筝名家的演奏会"></p>
<p>8月19日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_1.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_2.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_3.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家3"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_2.jpg" alt="金奖证书"></p>
<p><iframe height="498" width="510" src="http://player.youku.com/embed/XMzc5MzI2OTM0MA==" frameborder="0" 'allowfullscreen'=""></iframe><br>我的展演古筝曲目“伊犁河畔”</p>
]]></content>
    
